Run the program wordmatrixgen.py from a terminal window.  It will look in its directory for the config file for the matrix size.. In this case its hardcoded to be 16x16.  The cfg file is only to add the text to the button matrix.  

Click on the buttons you want to have active in the bitmap and click export.  Button clicks toggle the state of the button.

Look in the terminal window and copy the output.

See the wordmatrixgen_running.jpg to view an example of the output and application.

The matrix format is as follows:
